reviewText: We watch this movie every couple of years when the mood strikes us. Its a quirky Australian movie with lots of laughs. Unfortunatelyy I seem to have lost my copy in a move and don't want to buy a region 4 version just to watchh itt again.
I was hard to understand the cultural dialect.  I got the idea of the plot which is funny,  My husband is an active lawnbowler and he identified with the  uniforms and ritual involved in the game.
